==Usage==
* {{Tlx|PAGESINCATEGORY|Gallery}} gives {{PAGESINCATEGORY|Gallery}}
* {{Tlx|PAGESINCATEGORY|Gallery|R}} gives {{PAGESINCATEGORY|Gallery|R}}  (no commas)

This behaviour is the same as (and uses) the [[mw:Magic word]] "PAGESINCATEGORY".  The only exception is that if no parameter is used, the current pagename is used as the parameter.

